movieSeeds.title: Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2
movieSeeds.plot: The Guardians struggle to keep together as a team while dealing with their personal family issues, notably Star-Lord's encounter with his father the ambitious celestial being Ego.

movieSeeds.title: The Matrix
movieSeeds.plot: A computer hacker learns from mysterious rebels about the true nature of his reality and his role in the war against its controllers.

movieSeeds.title: Inception
movieSeeds.plot: A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a C.E.O.

movieSeeds.title: Van Helsing
movieSeeds.plot: The notorious monster hunter is sent to Transylvania to stop Count Dracula who is using Dr. Frankenstein's research and a werewolf for some sinister purpose.
